cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use these skills, please cite them as below."
title: "apostle-skills: exacting Agent Skills for serious thinking, reading, research, and translation"
abstract: >-
  A line of seven exacting Agent Skills for serious thinking, reading,
  research, and translation. It comprises a collaboration constitution
  (apostle-constitutio), a pre-draft nonfiction research method
  (apostle-article-research), a deep-reading protocol (apostle-opus-reading),
  three method-transplant satellites carrying verbatim French and Japanese kernels
  (apostle-opusmethodology-foucault-archaeology,
  apostle-opusmethodology-foucault-society-defended,
  apostle-opusmethodology-karatani-origins), and a low-variance literary and
  academic translation workflow (apostle-translation). Published by KL9 and
  Luciole Studio.
